description: This project will focus on enhancing capability in post harvest handling of grains through introducing, testing, and optimizing improved, new and appropriate post harvest technologies.

subproject.description:
Output 1 : Project management system established and agreed to; national project counterparts trained in project scope and post harvest technologies management. 
Output 2: Technologies introduced, tested, demonstrated and optimized. 
Output3: Capacities developed in good post harvest practice and in the management, maintenance and repair of equipment, Capacities developed  in loss assessment
subproject.title: Reduction of Post Harvest Loss

title: Reduction of Post Harvest Losses for Food Security
